Twinkle Khanna's wit and good looks catapult her to the top of the list of any man's ideal woman. When she and hubby Akshay Kumar were guests on this season of Koffee With Karan, not only did Karan Johar reveal that he had a crush on Twinkle during their school days, but it was also revealed that Akshay fell in love with her even though their relationship only started out as a fling.